{"tid":2085270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十月一日唔係end game，過左國安法都唔會係","createTime":"2020-06-29T19:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T20:32:19.000Z","uid":23058,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9be7b93cf9be174a27689caf2114eb5de4c2cf79","tid":2085270,"uid":23058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:55:32.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得上年10月1號嘅時候，曾經有一種氣氛覺得10月1號嘅行動係end game，但之後發生乜嘢事？<br />\n<br />\n中大保衛戰， Poly，醫護人員罷工，區選，仲有上上下下唔同戰線唔同崗位嘅手足繼續各自努力，為香港奮鬥。<br />\n<br />\n依家睇返起， 10月1日絕對唔係end game，而係一個開始。10月1中左槍傷嘅健仔，而家都仲繼續戰鬥緊，七月要繼續上庭。喺監獄嘅手足，佢哋都無放棄，依然期盼自由嘅來臨。<br />\n<br />\n從來反抗暴政都唔係一朝三夕嘅事，波蘭人抗共用咗40年，我哋只係啱啱開始。好似打機咁，我哋而家打大佬打到佢變咗第二型態，證明我哋之前嘅攻擊係有效。咁我哋更加唔能夠而家放棄，要打埋佢先會有贏嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n仲有希望大家唔好記得呢一張圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EDms4YwXkAAlylm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEDms4YwXkAAlylm.jpg&h=7c78980f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家而家放棄，我哋逝去嘅手足都一樣唔會原諒我哋。<br />\n<br />\n我哋而家正式進入第二階段，共勉之。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2b7bfe345226cea658bbcdda28b015ed9aead6","tid":2085270,"uid":101507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:57:23.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"d2a98b32e0b6c75f4b30174984b8004cfff838ad","tid":2085270,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T19:58:59.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"22d15ffb15d6789f337989c2b6bcf3ad362b691f","tid":2085270,"uid":23058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"67d9270b57f5eab0d7f8698653d7168e76f7ea97","tid":2085270,"uid":171684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:17:41.000Z","msg":"同意 推"},{"pid":"d63d9faa56621fcd0761be340f72d57c8df11180","tid":2085270,"uid":53027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"708cd55e2c5f75790c7f062a928e8ee6cdfd5222","tid":